I start with the Absolue serum all over my face followed by the Absolue eye cream under my eyes. Finally, I use the Absolue soft cream, an indulgent face cream that smooths the look of fine lines while visibly brightening and firming the skin. This luxurious cream delivers up to 24 hours of hydration for a luminous, plump appearance!
